erei 可能是最重要的 […]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-good-witches-of-pennsylvania/">《宾夕法尼亚的好女巫》</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> <i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Braucherei 是</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">阿米什人和门诺派社区使用的一种治疗形式，对于传统文化来说似乎是一种适当过时的做法。但作家雷切尔·约德 (Rachel Yoder) 回到门诺派根源，研究这种做法的现代用途。</span> <i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Braucherei</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">体现了备受讨论的阿米什社区的所有矛盾和复杂性，其</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">最重要的意义可能是因为它致力于一种古老的做法：有人尊重你的痛苦。 “还有什么比这更有价值的呢？”</span> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/1561977214&amp;color=%23ff5500&amp;auto_play=false&amp;hide_related=false&amp;show_comments=true&amp;show_user=true&amp;show_reposts=false&amp;show_teaser=true&amp;visual=true" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="no" scrolling="no"></iframe></p><div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"> <a style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" title="哈珀杂志" href="https://soundcloud.com/harpersmagazine" target="_blank" rel="noopener">哈珀杂志</a>· <a style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" title="宾夕法尼亚的好女巫" href="https://soundcloud.com/harpersmagazine/the-good-witches-of-pennsylvania" target="_blank" rel="noopener">宾夕法尼亚的好女巫</a></div><p>通过<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/the-harpers-podcast/id1405872370?mt=2">iTunes</a> 、 <a href="https://podcasts.google.com/feed/aHR0cHM6Ly9mZWVkcy5zb3VuZGNsb3VkLmNvbS91c2Vycy9zb3VuZGNsb3VkOnVzZXJzOjQ5OTE5MTM1L3NvdW5kcy5yc3M">Google Podcasts</a> 、 <a href="https://harpersmagazine.substack.com/s/the-harpers-podcast">Substack</a> 、 <a href="https://soundcloud.com/harpersmagazine">SoundCloud</a> 、 <a href="https://www.stitcher.com/podcast/harpers-magazine/the-harpers-podcast">Stitcher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.deezer.com/us/show/3364832">Deezer</a>或<a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/4h9SICTDppd1iJv9n5jXfc?si=zzWUGj8vQfaDJlzDaxmnwg">Spotify</a>订阅我们的播客。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-good-witches-of-pennsylvania/">《宾夕法尼亚的好女巫》</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-good-witches-of-pennsylvania/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments></item><item><title>每周回顾</title><link/>https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-climate-change-joe-biden-gun-violence-israel-palestine-eric-adams/<comments> https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-climate-change-joe-biden-gun-violence-israel-palestine-eric-adams/#respond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harper’s Magazine]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Tue, 11 Jul 2023 15:12:23 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Weekly Review]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://harpers.org/?p=287614 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p>据报道，一项民意调查发现，超过 40% 的美国人不知道七月四日纪念什么。</p><p>这篇<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-climate-change-joe-biden-gun-violence-israel-palestine-eric-adams/">《每周评论》</a>首先发表在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="drop-cap"><span style="font-weight: 400;">地球连续四天经历了有记录以来最热的一天，科学家将气候变化与人类大脑的萎缩联系起来。 <sup><a href="https://6abc.com/hottest-global-temperature-record-days-on-earth/13474129/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.sciencealert.com/new-paper-links-climate-change-to-shrinking-brain-size-in-humans?utm_source=fark&amp;utm_medium=website&amp;utm_content=link&amp;ICID=ref_fark" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2</a></sup> FDA 20 年来首次全面批准一种新的阿尔茨海默氏症药物，研究人员发现，与现有治疗方法相比，只有不到一半的新药具有实质性价值。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/06/health/alzheimers-leqembi-medicare.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">3</a> <a href="https://medicalxpress.com/news/2023-07-drugs-substantial-therapeutic-treatments.html?utm_source=fark&amp;utm_medium=website&amp;utm_content=link&amp;ICID=ref_fark" target="_blank" rel="noopener">4</a></sup> A poll was reported to have found that over 40 percent of Americans do not know what July Fourth commemorates, and mass shootings occurred in Pennsylvania, New York, North Carolina, Ohio, Louisiana, Oklahoma, Kansas, Missouri, Minnesota, California, Michigan, two cities in Indiana, two cities in Maryland, and twice in Fort Worth, Texas, the fewest in a Fourth of July weekend since 2019. <sup><a href="https://talker.news/2023/07/03/do-americans-know-the-true-meaning-of-independence-day/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">5</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.gunviolencearchive.org/reports/mass-shooting?page=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">6</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.gunviolencearchive.org/reports/mass-shooting?page=13&amp;year=2022" target="_blank" rel="noopener">7</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.gunviolencearchive.org/reports/mass-shooting?page=14&amp;year=2021" target="_blank" rel="noopener">8</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.gunviolencearchive.org/reports/mass-shooting?page=14&amp;year=2020" target="_blank" rel="noopener">9</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.gunviolencearchive.org/reports/mass-shooting?page=8&amp;year=2019" target="_blank" rel="noopener">10</a></sup> “We will not stop until we can finally and forever rid the world of this scourge,” said President Joe Biden, about the destruction of an M55 rocket filled with sarin nerve gas, the last remaining munition in the United States&#39; declared stockpile of chemical weapons, which marked the completion of a project that was originally scheduled for 2007 and that went 2,900 percent over budget. <sup><a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/07/07/statement-from-president-joe-biden-on-completing-the-destruction-of-the-united-states-chemical-weapons-stockpile/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">11</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://nypost.com/2023/07/07/biden-announces-us-chemical-weapons-stockpile-destroyed/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">12</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/06/us/chemical-weapons-stockpile.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">13</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/nceh/demil/history.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">14</a></sup>同一天，拜登宣布批准向乌克兰提供集束弹药，这些弹药旨在广泛散布“小炸弹”，其中 10％ 至 40％ 的炸弹失败，并可能在几十年后意外引爆。 <sup><a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/2023/07/06/biden-cluster-bombs-ukraine/?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=wp_main&amp;utm_medium=social" target="_blank" rel="noopener">15</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/07/07/europe/cluster-munitions-us-ukraine-aid-explainer-intl-hnk-ml/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">16</a></sup>这些武器被 123 个国家禁止，拜登前新闻秘书将其使用描述为“潜在的……战争罪”。 <sup><a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/press-briefings/2022/02/28/press-briefing-by-press-secretary-jen-psaki-february-28-2022/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">17</a></sup>据报道，在白宫西翼发现了可卡因。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/05/us/politics/white-house-cocaine.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">18</a></sup></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">以色列军队袭击了杰宁市两天，毁坏了汽车和房屋，用推土机毁坏了道路，并杀死了12名巴勒斯坦人，其中4人是未成年人。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/05/world/middleeast/israel-withdraws-jenin-west-bank.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">19</a></sup>在特拉维夫，一名巴勒斯坦人在撞车和刺伤袭击中造成 8 人受伤，随后被一名平民开枪射击；在耶路撒冷，法院宣判一名警察杀害一名患有自闭症巴勒斯坦男子的警察无罪。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/06/world/middleeast/iyad-al-hallaq-officer-acquitted-israel.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">20</a></sup>雇佣军领导人叶夫根尼·普里戈津 (Yevgeny Prigozhin) 在策划针对弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladimir Putin) 的兵变后同意流亡到白俄罗斯，他出现在圣彼得堡，据称俄罗斯安全部门已将一批武器和 100 亿卢布返还给他，据透露，美国前官员曾与俄罗斯知名人士就如何结束战争进行了秘密会谈。 <sup><a href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/exiled-wagner-boss-yevgeny-prigozhin-returns-to-russia-and-gets-his-weapons-back?ref=home?ref=home&amp;utm_source=fark&amp;utm_medium=website&amp;utm_content=link&amp;ICID=ref_fark" target="_blank" rel="noopener">21</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/former-us-officials-secret-ukraine-talks-russians-war-ukraine-rcna92610" target="_blank" rel="noopener">22</a></sup>荷兰政府在移民政策争议中垮台，据报道，英国一处收容无人陪伴儿童寻求庇护者的收容中心墙上的卡通人物壁画因为太受欢迎而被涂掉。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/07/world/europe/dutch-government-collapses.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">23</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2023/jul/07/robert-jenrick-has-cartoon-murals-painted-over-at-childrens-asylum-centre?utm_source=fark&amp;utm_medium=website&amp;utm_content=link&amp;ICID=ref_fark" target="_blank" rel="noopener">24</a></sup>温布尔登网球锦标赛的东道主警告与会者不要利用俱乐部安静的房间进行性行为，雷克瑟姆的一名护士在一名与她发生关系的病人被发现死在裤子里后被解雇。 <sup><a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2023/07/03/wimbledons-quiet-room-should-not-be-used-for-sex/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">25</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-66091127?utm_source=fark&amp;utm_medium=website&amp;utm_content=link&amp;ICID=ref_fark" target="_blank" rel="noopener">26</a></sup>在印度，警察推平了一名被指控向部落成员小便的男子的房屋；在加拿大，法院裁定竖起大拇指的表情符号视为接受合同。 <sup><a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/07/07/india/india-madhya-pradesh-home-demolished-urination-incident-intl-hnk/index.html?utm_source=twCNN&amp;utm_content=2023-07-07T09%3A44%3A49&amp;utm_term=link&amp;utm_medium=social" target="_blank" rel="noopener">27</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/07/world/canada/canada-thumbs-up-emoji-contract.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">28</a></sup></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯一再声称他的钱包里藏着一张死去警察的照片，据报道，他向一家报纸展示了一张他的工作人员打印出来的这名警察的照片，并用咖啡盖住了这张照片，以使其看起来很老。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/06/nyregion/mayor-adams-photo-venable-fake.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">29</a></sup>威斯康星州州长托尼·埃弗斯 (Tony Evers) 使用部分否决权删除了学校资助法案中的连字符和数字“20”，将其适用范围从 2024-25 学年延长至 2425 年，哈佛大学因其对捐赠者和遗产的招生偏好而被起诉。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/06/us/wisconsin-school-funding-400-years.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">30</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/07/03/us/harvard-college-legacy-admissions-lawsuit/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">31</a></sup>据报道，新泽西州一名法官因制作 TikTok 视频而受到调查，在该视频中，他衣着不整，穿着司法长袍，假唱下流歌曲。 “你觉得你可以跑到我身上来鞭打我的猴子屁股吗？”正义似乎在唱歌。 <sup><a href="https://www.complex.com/music/a/backwoodsaltar/judge-under-investigation-for-rapping-along-to-nas" target="_blank" rel="noopener">32</a></sup>在英国，一男一女在街上争夺一只鸭子的监护权；在伊利诺伊州，一名男子穿着兔子服抢劫了一家自助洗衣店；在俄亥俄州，一名穿着瓢虫连体衣的可疑商店扒手在一家商店周围追赶一名员工，并砸碎了两瓶酒。 <sup><a href="https://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/news/23637553.police-called-tatnam-road-poole-fight-duck/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">33</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.wfla.com/news/national/watch-furry-felon-robs-illinois-laundromat-dressed-in-full-bunny-suit/?utm_source=fark&amp;utm_medium=website&amp;utm_content=link&amp;ICID=ref_fark" target="_blank" rel="noopener">34</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://komonews.com/news/offbeat/suspect-wearing-onesie-smashes-wine-bottles-chases-employee-through-store-police-say-columbus-division-of-police-alcohol-liquor-booze-shooping-irate-angry-mad-upset?utm_source=fark&amp;utm_medium=website&amp;utm_content=link&amp;ICID=ref_fark" target="_blank" rel="noopener">35</a></sup>在佐治亚州，一名男子试图抢劫一家美甲店，但顾客和工作人员无视他，他就离开了。 <sup><a href="https://www.11alive.com/article/news/crime/video-patrons-robber-atlanta-nail-salon-police-suspect/85-4780230c-7320-417c-9c4a-815471405929" target="_blank" rel="noopener">36</a></sup>一名八年前被报告失踪的德克萨斯人被发现一直与他的母亲住在一起，一名在罗马斗兽场上刻下对女友的爱情宣言的游客道歉说，他没有意识到这座建筑很古老。 <sup><a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/07/06/us/rudy-farias-mother-found-home/index.html?utm_term=link&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twcnnbrk&amp;utm_content=2023-07-06T17%3A28%3A39" target="_blank" rel="noopener">37</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/05/world/europe/tourist-colosseum-rome-apology.html?utm_source=pocket_saves" target="_blank" rel="noopener">38</a></sup>据报道，爱荷华州一名妇女接到警报说她的房子着火了，在回家的路上发生摩托车事故，导致多处骨头骨折，在医院时被诊断出患有癌症。 <sup><a href="https://www.kcci.com/article/house-fire-motorcycle-crash-was-the-start-of-a-bad-sunday-for-iowa-couple/44434078" target="_blank" rel="noopener">39</a></sup>一辆公共汽车在澳大利亚安全海滩坠毁。 <sup><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2023/jul/05/mornington-peninsula-bus-crash-houses-safety-beach-dromana-parade" target="_blank" rel="noopener">40——</a></sup></span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">乔恩·埃德尔曼</span></i></p><p>这篇<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-climate-change-joe-biden-gun-violence-israel-palestine-eric-adams/">《每周评论》</a>首先发表在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-climate-change-joe-biden-gun-violence-israel-palestine-eric-adams/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments></item><item><title>每周回顾</title><link/>https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-french-protests-supreme-court-desantis-eric-adams-vaccines-robert-kennedy/<comments> https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-french-protests-supreme-court-desantis-eric-adams-vaccines-robert-kennedy/#respond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harper’s Magazine]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 06 Jul 2023 15:18:08 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Weekly Review]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://harpers.org/?p=287471 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> “我们认为这只是，空气通过你的鼻孔，你就会移动。不，呼吸是有科学的。”</p><p>这篇<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-french-protests-supreme-court-desantis-er