get="_blank" rel="noopener">28</a></sup></span><span style="font-weight: 400;">一辆运载牛的卡车和一辆运载墨西哥卷饼的卡车在内布拉斯加州相撞。 <sup><a href="https://www.ketv.com/article/holy-cow-cattle-truck-and-burrito-truck-collide-causing-beefy-backup-on-i-80-for-7-hours/44391360" target="_blank" rel="noopener">29</a></sup>威斯康星州一辆发生故障的过山车导致乘客倒挂数小时。 <sup><a href="https://www.wsaz.com/2023/07/03/roller-coaster-riders-trapped-upside-down-hours/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">30</a></sup>考古学家宣布，他们在庞贝古城发现了一幅 2000 年前的画，描绘了一块大饼，一名游客因将他和他女朋友的姓名首字母刻在罗马斗兽场的外部而被捕。 <sup><a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-66031341" target="_blank" rel="noopener">31</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://news.artnet.com/art-world/arrested-colosseum-vandal-apologizes-2331310" target="_blank" rel="noopener">32</a></sup> Joey</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">“Jaws” Chestnut 第 16 次赢得全国吃热狗大赛冠军。 <sup><a href="https://ca.sports.yahoo.com/news/joey-chestnut-wins-16th-hot-204800087.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">33——</a></sup></span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">梅根·埃弗希德</span></i></p><p>这篇<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-french-protests-supreme-court-desantis-eric-adams-vaccines-robert-kennedy/">《每周评论》</a>首先发表在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://harpers.org/2023/07/weekly-review-french-protests-supreme-court-desantis-eric-adams-vaccines-robert-kennedy/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments></item><item><title>末日机器</title><link/>https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-doomsday-machine/<comments> https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-doomsday-machine/#respond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jackson Lears]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 03 Jul 2023 10:00:23 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Podcast]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nuclear warfare]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://harpers.org/?p=287469 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p>美国现在不是早晨：关于核冬天的持续威胁</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-doomsday-machine/">《末日机器》</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="drop-cap"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">《原子科学家公报》的世界末日时钟从未如此接近午夜，但 20 世纪 60 年代的核恐慌却仿佛成为了历史。杰克逊·李尔斯（Jackson Lears）曾在冷战期间在一艘核武装船上担任海军军官，他讨论了我们如何接受技术力量的神话，使自己摆脱战争的恐怖。他写道：“战争是人类所能进行的最不可预测、最难控制的事业，但我们却对它给予了最多的技术敬意。”</span></p><p> https://soundcloud.com/harpersmagazine/the-doomsday-machine</p><h3 class="archive-desc">通过<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/the-harpers-podcast/id1405872370?mt=2">iTunes</a> 、 <a href="https://podcasts.google.com/feed/aHR0cHM6Ly9mZWVkcy5zb3VuZGNsb3VkLmNvbS91c2Vycy9zb3VuZGNsb3VkOnVzZXJzOjQ5OTE5MTM1L3NvdW5kcy5yc3M">Google Podcasts</a> 、 <a href="https://harpersmagazine.substack.com/s/the-harpers-podcast">Substack</a> 、 <a href="https://soundcloud.com/harpersmagazine">SoundCloud</a> 、 <a href="https://www.stitcher.com/podcast/harpers-magazine/the-harpers-podcast">Stitcher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.deezer.com/us/show/3364832">Deezer</a>或<a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/4h9SICTDppd1iJv9n5jXfc?si=zzWUGj8vQfaDJlzDaxmnwg">Spotify</a>订阅我们的播客。</h3><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-doomsday-machine/">《末日机器》</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-doomsday-machine/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments></item><item><title>每周回顾</title><link/>https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-wagner-group-prigozhin- Russia-coup-belarus-prince-harry/<comments> https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-wagner-group-prigozhin- Russia-coup-belarus-prince-harry/#respond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harper’s Magazine]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Tue, 27 Jun 2023 18:03:46 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Weekly Review]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://harpers.org/?p=287458 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p>据报道，哈佛大学一名研究不诚实问题的研究员被指控捏造数据。</p><p>这篇<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-wagner-group-prigozhin-russia-coup-belarus-prince-harry/">《每周评论》</a>首先发表在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="drop-cap"><span style="font-weight: 400;">弗拉基米尔·普京总统执政二十年来面临的最大挑战是，在入侵乌克兰时与俄罗斯军队并肩作战的瓦格纳集团雇佣兵占领了顿河畔罗斯托夫的军事总部，并开始向莫斯科进军，要求解雇国防部长谢尔盖·绍伊古。 <sup><a href="https://www.theday.com/world/20230625/challenge-to-putin-fizzles-as-foe-orders-retreat-goes-into-exile/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1</a> <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-60947877" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2</a> <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/live/2023/06/24/world/russia-wagner-prigozhin-ukraine-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener">3</a> <a href="https://www.pbs.org/newshour/world/prigozhin-orders-wagner-mercenaries-to-halt-march-on-moscow-retreat-from-russia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">4</a></sup> “如果有人妨碍我们，我们将摧毁一切，”瓦格纳集团的领导人、前热狗小贩叶夫根尼·普里戈任 (Yevgeny Prigozhin) 说道，他此前曾将高级军事官员描述为“该死的母狗”，“他妈的会在地狱里吃掉[阵亡士兵]的内脏！” <sup><a href="https://www.politico.eu/article/putin-in-crisis-as-wagner-chief-prigozhin-declares-war-on-russian-military-leadership/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">5</a> <a href="https://english.elpais.com/international/2023-06-24/yevgeny-prigozhin-from-a-hot-dog-stand-in-st-petersburg-to-leading-a-rebellion-against-putin.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">6</a> <a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/jester-or-rebel-mercenary-prigozhin-lays-bare-strains-putins-war-2023-05-23/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">7</a></sup>危机开始后不到 24 小时，白俄罗斯总统亚历山大·卢卡申科促成了一项协议，即撤销对普里戈任的指控，以换取他流亡白俄罗斯，参与的瓦格纳部队将不会受到起诉，而未参加的瓦格纳战士将获得与俄罗斯国防部的合同，瓦格纳雇佣战士停止了行军。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/24/world/europe/russia-wagner-prigozhin.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">8</a></sup> “谈话很艰难，而且据我所知，谈话充满男性气概，”一位白俄罗斯分析师在研究卢卡申科和普里戈任之间的谈话时表示。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/25/world/europe/belarus-lukashenko-russia-wagner.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">9</a></sup> “他们立即脱口而出如此粗俗的话，会让任何母亲哭泣。” “以色列是一个法治国家。公民都有义务遵守法律，”总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡 (Benjamin Netanyahu) 说道，他宣布了在约旦河西岸建造 1,000 套新住房的计划。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/21/world/middleeast/west-bank-settlement-palestinian-israeli-violence.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">10</a></sup>美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普声称，他向图书出版商展示的那些他所说的“高度机密”的文件实际上是新闻剪报。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/19/us/politics/trump-classified-document-fox-news.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">11</a></sup>据透露，哈里王子希望与特朗普和普京一起制作播客，讨论童年创伤。 <sup><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-06-22/prince-harry-s-podcast-pitch-to-spotify-talk-to-putin-trump-about-childhoods" target="_blank" rel="noopener">12</a></sup></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">大约 500 名试图逃离巴基斯坦、叙利亚和埃及的移民在地中海因过度拥挤的阿德里安娜号翻船沉没而丧生，希腊海岸警卫队因没有试图营救这艘渔船而受到密切</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">关注</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/19/world/europe/greece-migrants-ship-sinking.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">13</a> <a href="https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/greek-coast-guard-questioned-over-response-to-deadly-sinking-of-migrant-vessel" target="_blank" rel="noopener">14</a></sup>希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯 (Kyriakos Mitsotakis) 的反移民立场支撑了他最近的选举胜利，他指责走私者，并称他们为“可怜的……人渣”。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/19/world/asia/pakistan-mourning-greece-migrant-ship.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">15</a></sup>在与潜水器母船失去联系后，美国海岸警卫队、加拿大海岸警卫队、美国海军、加拿大皇家海军、美国空军、加拿大皇家空军、法国救援队和私人船只搜寻泰坦尼克号，船上载有五人，其中三人每人向深海勘探公司 OceanGate 支付了 25 万美元，以参观泰坦尼克号</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">的</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">残骸</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">。</span></i> <sup><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-023-02074-x" target="_blank" rel="noopener">16</a> <a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/opinions/2023/6/21/titan-and-the-trawler-whose-lives-matter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">17</a></span></sup> <span style="font-weight: 400;"><sup><a href="https://en.as.com/latest_news/missing-titan-submarine-how-much-does-the-search-and-rescue-mission-cost-and-whos-paying-for-it-n-2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">18</a></sup>救援人员在面积是康涅狄格州两倍、深度 2.5 英里的区域搜寻了这艘飞船，这艘飞船尚未获得安全认证，并引起了三打以上行业领袖、探险家和海洋学家的警告，由 OceanGate 首席执行官、美国百万富翁斯托克顿·拉什 (Stockton Rush) 驾驶，他曾说过，“在某些时候，安全纯粹是浪费。” <sup><a href="https://www.khou.com/video/news/nation-world/sub-titanic-search/285-570cc76a-2293-4014-9315-dc9ac00d2751" target="_blank" rel="noopener">19</a> <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/20/us/oceangate-titanic-missing-submersible.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">20</a> <a href="https://www.distractify.com/p/stockton-rush-net-worth" target="_blank" rel="noopener">21</a> <a href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/missing-titanic-sub-plagued-by-a-long-history-of-deadly-safety-issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">22</a></sup>四天后，</span>发现了<i><span style="font-weight: 400;">泰坦号</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">的残骸，得出的结论是，这艘船遭受了“灾难性的内爆”，船上的所有人都丧生，其中包括拉什，他写道：“我们经常听到‘你要杀人’这样毫无根据的叫喊声。我认为这是严重的个人侮辱。” <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/live/2023/06/22/us/titanic-missing-submarine" target="_blank" rel="noopener">23</a> <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-65998914" target="_blank" rel="noopener">24</a> “我们的心与这五个灵魂同在，”OceanGate 在一份声明中写道。 <sup><a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/titan-submarine-dead-missing-titanic-1235649790/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">25</a></sup></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">得梅因的一名气象学家因报道气候变化而受到死亡威胁后辞职。 <sup><a href="https://www.rawstory.com/chris-gloninger/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">26</a></sup>德克萨斯州州长格雷格·阿博特签署废除要求建筑工人休息和喝水的规定六天后，一名公用事业线路工人因中暑死亡。 <sup><a href="https://jordanbarab.com/confinedspace/2023/06/21/worker-dies-of-heat-stroke-6-days-after-abbott-signs-bill-repealing-heat-protections/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">27</a></sup>澳大利亚否决了在堪培拉设立俄罗斯大使馆的计划后，一名据信是俄罗斯外交官的男子被发现蹲在建筑工地上。 <sup><a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/squatting-russian-diplomat-australia-embassy-standoff-canberra-rcna90740" target="_blank" rel="noopener">28</a></sup>据报道，哈佛大学一名研究不诚实问题的研究员被指控捏造数据。 <sup><a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-12230013/Harvard-behavioral-scientist-studies-dishonesty-accused-fabricating-data.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">29日，</a></sup>联邦快递被指控里程表欺诈，据透露，波音公司向军方收取了近5.2万美元的垃圾桶费用。 <sup><a href="https://jalopnik.com/fedex-named-in-what-could-be-one-of-the-largest-odomete-1850570768" target="_blank" rel="noopener">30</a> <a href="https://responsiblestatecraft.org/2023/06/20/the-pentagons-52000-trash-can/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">31</a></sup>一名韩国青少年在飞机飞行时试图打开飞机紧急门，结果被机组人员套住；据报道，一名纳什维尔妇女在短期出租屋内发现一名成年陌生人睡在她的孩子们中间。 <sup><a href="https://www.indiatoday.in/world/story/flight-crew-lassoes-restrains-south-korean-teen-trying-open-plane-door-mid-air-2395690-2023-06-21" target="_blank" rel="noopener">32</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.wsmv.com/2023/06/22/man-caught-sleeping-between-children-nashville-short-term-rental-property/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">33</a></sup>印第安纳波利斯一名男子被指控抢劫一名妇女并强迫她在 Facebook 上添加他，据报道后来向她提出约会。 <sup><a href="https://www.kmov.com/2023/06/22/man-robbed-woman-gunpoint-then-asked-her-date-records-show/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">34</a></sup>心理学家发现，伴侣性行为可以改善睡眠，但自慰却不能。 <sup><a href="https://www.psypost.org/2023/06/partnered-sexual-activity-with-orgasm-improves-sleep-study-finds-165931" target="_blank" rel="noopener">35</a></sup>俄亥俄州禁止配偶强奸的法案仍被委员会搁置。 <sup><a href="https://www.news5cleveland.com/news/local-news/once-again-state-lawmakers-consider-bill-to-make-spousal-rape-illegal-in-ohio" target="_blank" rel="noopener">36</a></sup> “我认为这不是一个好主意。但我不认为我想投票阻止它，”据报道，特拉华州众议院议长在谈到允许企业投票的提案时说道。 <sup><a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/seaford-delaware-corporate-voting-llc-trust-elections/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">37</a></sup> “对我来说，她确实是一个令人讨厌的小泼妇”，马乔里·泰勒·格林 (Marjorie Taylor Greene) 在解释为什么她在众议院会场上称她的自由核心小组成员劳伦·博伯特 (Lauren Boebert) 为“小泼妇”时说道。 <sup><a href="https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2023/01/23/freedom-caucus-likely-to-play-a-bigger-role-in-new-gop-led-house-so-who-are-they/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">38</a></sup> <sup><a href="https://www.semafor.com/article/06/21/2023/greene-boebert-little-b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">39</a></sup>埃隆·马斯克和马克·扎克伯格同意进行一场笼斗。 <sup><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/22/business/musk-zuckerberg-cage-match.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">40</a></sup> —</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">乔恩·埃德尔曼</span></i></p><p>这篇<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-wagner-group-prigozhin-russia-coup-belarus-prince-harry/">《每周评论》</a>首先发表在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-wagner-group-prigozhin- Russia-coup-belarus-prince-harry/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments></item><item><title>泰坦之后</title><link/>https://harpers.org/2023/06/after-the-titan-oceangate-disaster-implosion-stockton-rush/<comments> https://harpers.org/2023/06/after-the-titan-oceangate-disaster-implosion-stockton-rush/#respond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[Matthew Gavin Frank]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Tue, 27 Jun 2023 17:23:53 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Podcast]]></category><category><![CDATA[Deep sea diving]]></category><category><![CDATA[OceanGate]]></category><category><![CDATA[Titan (submersible)]]></category><category><![CDATA[Titanic (Ship)]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://harpers.org/?p=287457 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p>作者反思自己在业余潜水器中的经历</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/06/after-the-titan-oceangate-disaster-implosion-stockton-rush/">《泰坦之后》</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="drop-cap"><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">泰坦</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">潜水器上周发生内爆</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">后</span>，马修·加文·弗兰克与斯托克顿·拉什的朋友卡尔·斯坦利的深海之旅有了新的意义。 <span style="font-weight: 400;">（弗兰克今年二月乘坐过斯坦利的潜艇； <a href="https://harpers.org/archive/2023/07/submersion-journalism-homemade-submarine-honduras-deep-sea-diving" target="_blank" rel="noopener">他的文章</a>在海洋之门潜艇失踪后的第二天就在网上发表，其中弗兰克沉思了深海探索的永恒危险和诱惑。）他讨论了斯坦利对拉什的警告、大规模恐惧以及他是否对自己的经历感到遗憾。</span> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="哈珀杂志《泰坦之后》" width="500" height="400" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?visual=true&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F1551432964&#038;show_artwork=true&#038;maxheight=750&#038;maxwidth=500"></iframe></p><h3 class="archive-desc">通过<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/the-harpers-podcast/id1405872370?mt=2">iTunes</a> 、 <a href="https://podcasts.google.com/feed/aHR0cHM6Ly9mZWVkcy5zb3VuZGNsb3VkLmNvbS91c2Vycy9zb3VuZGNsb3VkOnVzZXJzOjQ5OTE5MTM1L3NvdW5kcy5yc3M">Google Podcasts</a> 、 <a href="https://harpersmagazine.substack.com/s/the-harpers-podcast">Substack</a> 、 <a href="https://soundcloud.com/harpersmagazine">SoundCloud</a> 、 <a href="https://www.stitcher.com/podcast/harpers-magazine/the-harpers-podcast">Stitcher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.deezer.com/us/show/3364832">Deezer</a>或<a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/4h9SICTDppd1iJv9n5jXfc?si=zzWUGj8vQfaDJlzDaxmnwg">Spotify</a>订阅我们的播客。</h3><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/06/after-the-titan-oceangate-disaster-implosion-stockton-rush/">《泰坦之后》</a>一文首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://harpers.org/2023/06/after-the-titan-oceangate-disaster-implosion-stockton-rush/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments></item><item><title>每周回顾</title><link/>https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-titan-oceangate-trump/<comments> https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-titan-oceangate-trump/#respond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harper’s Magazine]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Wed, 21 Jun 2023 17:02:51 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Weekly Review]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://harpers.org/?p=287442 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p>一位比利时心理学家发现，大多数成年人都患有“历史终结幻觉”。</p><p>这篇<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-titan-oceangate-trump/">《每周评论》</a>首先发表在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="drop-cap"><span style="font-weight: 400;">泰坦</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">号是</span></i>一艘业余潜水器，其乘客包括英国行动航空公司主席和英国亿万富翁及其儿子。<i><span style="font-weight: 400;">泰坦</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">号在巡视泰坦尼克号残骸时在加拿大海岸失踪，并开始了大规模的搜救工作</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">。 <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-65934887"><sup>1</sup></a> <a href="https://gulfnews.com/world/asia/pakistan/pakistani-billionaire-and-his-son-among-five-aboard-missing-titanic-submarine-1.96516384"><sup>2</sup></a> “这似乎是我们见过的最严重的悲剧，”一名欧盟官员在谈到希腊海岸一艘移民船沉没事件时表示，该事件导致至少 300 名试图逃离本国数十年来最严重经济危机的巴基斯坦公民丧生。 <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/06/18/asia/pakistan-deaths-migrant-boat-disaster-greece-intl-hnk/index.html"><sup>3</sup></a> <a href="https://www.news8000.com/news/national-world/greek-migrant-boat-wreck-may-be-mediterranean-s-worst-ever-tragedy-with-hundreds-still-missing/article_facb21d8-a917-5af7-aefd-ea4d588dad22.html"><sup>4</sup></a>在马萨诸塞州，执法部门组织的“DNA Drive Day”活动因恶劣天气和美国公民自由联盟提出的担忧而被推迟，该活动声称他们将利用收集的基因数据来解决悬案。 <a href="https://apnews.com/article/public-dna-collection-massachussetts-32824ce94a782dec91023090a812e0f9"><sup>5</sup></a>据报道，箭牌口香糖财富的继承人和一位制作了多部亚当·桑德勒电影的美国金融家都在争夺 Pegasus 间谍软件背后的以色列公司的控股权，该公司已被世界各国政府用来监视记者，包括贾迈勒·卡舒吉的妻子。 <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/jun/14/nso-group-spyware-pegasus-takeover"><sup>6</sup></a> <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/sep/22/jamal-khashoggis-wife-to-sue-nso-group-over-pegasus-spyware"><sup>7</sup></a>国防分析师丹尼尔·埃尔斯伯格 (Daniel Ellsberg) 于 1970 年在 13 岁儿子的帮助下复印了 7,000 页五角大楼机密文件，最终在亲人的陪伴下去世，享年 92 岁。 <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/16/us/daniel-ellsberg-dead.html"><sup>8</sup></a> <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/28/nyregion/pentagon-papers-robert-ellsberg.html"><sup>9</sup></a>在埋葬第一任妻子的新泽西高尔夫球场，唐纳德·特朗普对他的第二份起诉书进行了猛烈抨击，其中包括 31 项违反《间谍法》的行为，并称赞他的五个孩子中的三个是“严肃的人”。 <a href="https://nymag.com/intelligencer/article/ivana-trump-buried-bedminster-3-theories.html"><sup>10</sup></a> <a href="https://www.politico.com/interactives/2023/trump-criminal-investigations-cases-tracker-list/"><sup>11</sup></a></span> <span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.rev.com/blog/transcripts/trump-responds-to-charges-in-speech-following-arraignment-in-federal-court-transcript"><sup>12</sup></a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">土库曼斯坦的家族统治国家近20年，总统宣布大规模打击吸烟，南非税务局宣布将在一场大火中销毁约2000万支走私香烟，价值230万美元，官员称这场大火“可能会持续几天”。 <a href="https://www.yahoo.com/news/turkmenistan-vows-end-smoking-within-111618400.html"><sup>13</sup></a> <a href="https://www.yahoo.com/news/smoke-africa-destroys-20-mn-182623013.html"><sup>14</sup></a> “瑞吉斯行动”阻止了向新西兰运送 1,572 磅冰毒，这些冰毒被藏在枫糖浆瓶中。 <a href="https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2023/06/15/new-zealand-meth-inception-maple-syrup-bottles/70324891007/"><sup>15</sup></a>加州劳工部官员对萨克拉门托一家快餐店处以罚款，该店在因盗窃工资而接受调查时，邀请工人向一名假牧师坦白，而后者却对他们进行盘问，例如他们是否在工作中偷过任何东西。 <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/16/us/priest-workplace-confessions-wage-theft-california.html"><sup>16 日，</sup></a>英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 由于时间安排冲突而错过了有关制裁鲍里斯·约翰逊 (Boris Johnson) 的议会辩论，他在推特上表示，唐宁街 10 号前门出现的二进制代码是为了纪念伦敦科技周。 <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2023/jun/19/rishi-sunak-to-miss-vote-sanctioning-boris-johnson-over-partygate"><sup>17</sup></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RishiSunak/status/1669002908807954432"><sup>18</sup></a>一位保守派媒体评论家和多伦多市长候选人曾表示“我竞选的一切对我来说都是真实的”，但在一名记者注意到其中一张逼真图像中的一名女性至少有三只手臂后，他被指控使用人工智能制作竞选广告。 <a href="https://globalnews.ca/news/9779953/anthony-furey-toronto-mayoral-election/"><sup>19</sup></a> <a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/xgwwmk/anti-homeless-mayoral-candidate-uses-ai-to-create-fake-images-of-blight"><sup>20</sup></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/BenSpurr/status/1668355886606082081"><sup>21</sup></a>一位比利时心理学家发现，大多数成年人都患有“历史终结幻觉”。 <a href="https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20230619-how-the-end-of-history-illusion-shapes-your-life-choices"><sup>22</sup></a> <a href="https://www.esade.edu/faculty/jordi.quoidbach"><sup>23</sup></a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">哈佛医学院附属太平间的经理被联邦检察官指控盗窃和出售捐赠尸体的身体部位，并收到写有“braiiiiiis”和“7号头”的收据。 <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/14/us/harvard-medical-school-body-parts.html?searchResultPosition=1"><sup>24</sup></a>波兰基督教团体成功向当地一家公交车运营商施压，将其之前开往波罗的海沿海小镇赫尔的 666 路公交车更名为 669 路公交车。 <a href="https://apnews.com/article/poland-bus-hel-666-e4443f1b245b4486b9180849f1317fc1"><sup>25</sup></a>路易斯安那州警方在谈到一名 28 岁洪都拉斯妇女时表示，“这背后并没有任何邪恶的原因”。这名女子非法伪造了出生证明，以便以 17 岁的新生身份进入当地高中入学，以提高英语水平。 <a href="https://apnews.com/article/louisiana-student-imposter-woman-arrest-8b9748664c343a2d54391f770a84fcbf"><sup>26</sup></a>一名芝加哥男子四月份从梦中醒来，梦见有人闯入他的家，用 0.357 Magnum 左轮手枪射击自己的腿，现在他被指控非法持有枪支。 <a href="https://apnews.com/article/illinois-man-shoots-self-dream-intruder-0ac5fa2d975bb4e68ad9e4eae47290f2"><sup>27</sup></a>宾夕法尼亚州立大学的一名教授因涉嫌在州立公园步道上被狗舔肛门而被捕，他说：“我这样做是为了发泄一下。” “我要做什么才能让你向我开枪？” <a href="https://www.insidehighered.com/news/quick-takes/2023/06/16/penn-state-professor-leave-after-found-compromising-position-dog"><sup>28</sup></a> —</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">玛雅·佩里</span></i></p><p>这篇<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-titan-oceangate-trump/">《每周评论》</a>首先发表在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">《哈珀杂志》</a>上。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://harpers.org/2023/06/weekly-review-titan-oceangate-trump/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments></item><item><title> The DIY Submariner</title><link/> https://harpers.org/2023/06/the-diy-submariner/<comments> https://harpers.org/2023/06/the-diy-submariner/#respond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[Violet Lucca]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Tue, 20 Jun 2023 12:00:10 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Podcast]]></category><category><![CDATA[Submarine]]></category><category><![CDATA[Submarines (Ships)]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://harpers.org/?p=287423 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> Realizing the eternal dream of journeying into the briny depths—on your own terms</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/06/the-diy-submariner/">The DIY Submariner</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">Harper&#39;s Magazine</a> .</p> ]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="drop-cap"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Exploring 2,000 feet below the sea&#39;s surface is something only professionals—or billionaires—are able to do. However, the writer <a href="https://harpers.org/archive/2023/07/submersion-journalism-homemade-submarine-honduras-deep-sea-diving" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Matthew Gavin Frank</a> found Karl Stanley, an eccentric submariner, to take him to the depths in a DIY sub off the coast of Honduras. Frank dived to the bottom of the sea against his own anxieties and explored not only bioluminescence and sharks, but also the sublimity of being “completely quieted” as a writer.</span> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The DIY Submariner by Harper’s Magazine" width="500" height="400" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?visual=true&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F1542117052&#038;show_artwork=true&#038;maxheight=750&#038;maxwidth=500"></iframe></p><h3 class="archive-desc"> Subscribe to our podcast through <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/the-harpers-podcast/id1405872370?mt=2">iTunes</a> , <a href="https://podcasts.google.com/feed/aHR0cHM6Ly9mZWVkcy5zb3VuZGNsb3VkLmNvbS91c2Vycy9zb3VuZGNsb3VkOnVzZXJzOjQ5OTE5MTM1L3NvdW5kcy5yc3M">Google Podcasts<